{"tid":95293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年三十晚上11時，光復年宵","createTime":"2017-01-26T01:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T17:05:19.000Z","uid":24140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89b1b317674d7f7aaa9f93f1a0aefd7a1767bc8e","tid":95293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:58:43.000Z","msg":"警方高度重視「光復年宵」海報　維園將採取人流管制<br />\n陳曉慶報道<br />\n食環署在維園年宵市場外的閘口和石柱，發現有人張貼匿名海報，聲稱於年三十晚進行「光復年宵」行動。警方高度重視事件，已展開情報搜集和分析，以了解涉及那些團體。<br />\n<br />\n消息透露，食環署職員昨日下午在維園發現有人張貼海報，上面寫有「年三十晚上11時，光復年宵」的字眼，但並無註明發起的組織名稱。<br />\n<br />\n消息表示，保安部門高度重視事件，認為維園年三十晚人流非常擠逼，若發生意外，後果不堪設想。當局會確保公眾安全及秩序，採取人流管制措施，令市民有秩序進出維園。另外，鑑於去年發生的旺角騷亂事件，警方今年將作出更嚴密和審慎部署，據了解今年會部署約1500名警力，在年三十至年初四期間候命，並在港島及西九龍多個地點加強巡邏。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1310011-20170126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1310011-20170126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=4ce14ab4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1310011-20170126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=059cfc2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1310011-20170126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e1e48f833997e198feb29394c7a7cc4cff31880f","tid":95293,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a513303571a9ccceddef242751be50dc31036a3","tid":95293,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629182584f0f5effa9b8fa6bc26bc96a8ae5e72c","tid":95293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"c01847f2f037adcb7803c0ad778fd4c064c9ccb4","tid":95293,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"開始多人"},{"pid":"316468b13deeddcae7d624d921f57449d6367f38","tid":95293,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61903a4e9a1fd45d06530807e2c2a88b335e3b2","tid":95293,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來吳聖人2個月前先至老來得子，俗語有話差人愛邪牌，大家又估下佢老婆係咪蝗族呢可？？？有冇驗DNA咁呢？？？</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F010442_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a027e16b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170125/photo/bkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170125233803\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170125%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170125215842764-0125_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170125233803&h=bd7f06a4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n被廉署拘捕另外2名警務人員，其中高級督察陳嘉健為港大尖子，被視為警隊「明日之星」，另一名反黑探員鍾文浩曾是臥底黑幫的「無間道」，去年獲盧偉聰頒發處長嘉許狀。陳和鍾同樣都有反黑經驗及與「O記」有交集。<br />\n<br />\n年僅28歲的陳，被捕前駐守有組織罪案及三合會調查科，他2012年曾接受傳媒訪問，親述投考警隊的經歷，表明身為督察須有熱誠，認為即使面對困難亦不能退縮，且要有承擔去完成每一個任務。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉健2010年畢業於香港大學工程系，大學二年級時參加警隊學長計劃後，立志加入警隊。他後來透過「警務督察招募快線」投考督察，畢業前已通過警隊考核程序，並在畢業後隨即接受警察學院36周的訓練，先擔任軍裝巡邏小隊指揮官，再轉往旺角警區刑事調查隊，曾駐守旺角警區反黑組，其後調任有組織罪案及三合會調查科。<br />\n<br />\n33歲的偵緝警員鍾文浩，2010年11月獲「O記」招攬，滲入黑幫作臥底搜證，協助偵破屯門黑幫「新X安」一宗廝殺案，案中綽號「郭靖」的18歲青年被人用刀襲擊及用汽車輾過死亡，警方其後拘捕疑兇。鍾文浩於2014年6月，以臥底警員身份上庭作供。2016年6月23日，鍾獲警務處處長盧偉聰頒予嘉許狀。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233905_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=32e28bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233932_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff2cf913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F233951_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6c125857&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234001_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e099270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5487b47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234026_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8c6ed135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F234040_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e1fbaed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F000623_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=15f6a296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F001642_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a7be1cb3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca22fc22f724944eff65a51724db166c2f4165f4","tid":95293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"7fc09dcf8f5dda8d03c660aec002fab596e4a45c","tid":95293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"002215d5a6f86222fa137dfb50b11dad03ca17b1","tid":95293,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oEjHTpdpGo1vGQRby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=81614293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o7TKyRvIBycoKY8so%2Fsource.gif&h=c6e30b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.giphy.com/26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.giphy.com%2F26FPsF6AnUBwnqdos.gif&h=f7613e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26FPnpatcd94T0JLW/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26FPnpatcd94T0J